<p><%= @first_user.first_name %> and <%= @second_user.first_name %>,</p>

<p>Congrats! Both of you expressed interest in meeting up. Be sure to schedule a call or coordinate a time and place to meet soon. Both of you are located in the <%= @first_user.location.area %>.</p>

<% if @shared_connections_count > 1 %>
  <p>You have <%= @shared_connections_count %> shared connections on LinkedIn.</p>
<% end %>

<div>
  <div style="display: inline-block">
    <div><%= image_tag @first_user.image, size: '150x150' %></div>
    <div><%= @first_user.name %></div>
    <div><%= @first_user.headline %></div>
  </div>

  <div style="display: inline-block"></div>

  <div style="display: inline-block">
    <div><%= image_tag @second_user.image, size: '150x150' %></div>
    <div><%= @second_user.name %></div>
    <div><%= @second_user.headline %></div>
  </div>
</div>

<p>-The SwiftIntro Team</p>
